@startuml
title Community service - user search and profile preview

actor User
participant "Community page" as FE
participant "gRPC Gateway\nUserRoutes" as Gateway
participant "Community UserGrpc" as UserGrpc
participant "UserService" as UserService
database "MongoDB" as Mongo

User -> FE : opens Community tab
FE -> Gateway : GET /v1/users?page=1&page_size=50&search=query
Gateway -> UserGrpc : ListUsers(filter, pagination)
UserGrpc -> UserService : list_users(filter, pagination)
UserService -> Mongo : query users by search/filter
Mongo --> UserService : users + total_count
UserService -> UserService : map documents to UserResponse[]
UserService --> UserGrpc : ListUsersResponse
UserGrpc --> Gateway : ListUsersResponse
Gateway --> FE : users list

User -> FE : clicks Add friend / preview
FE -> Gateway : GET /v1/users/{selected_user_id}
Gateway -> UserGrpc : GetUser(id)
UserGrpc -> UserService : get_user(id)
UserService -> Mongo : find user
Mongo --> UserService : user document
UserService --> UserGrpc : UserResponse
UserGrpc --> Gateway : UserResponse
Gateway --> FE : profile preview data
FE -> FE : render mini profile preview + link to /users/{id}

@enduml
